rComments: The class is the definition of bird course!  Although a formal essay is required (35%).

Had her for summer of 2010, just to see if it was a bird course, and I had experience playing the piano so I thought it was a no brainer. Had a LOT of memorization of dates of songs titles and artists. And also listening song identification. Studied hard for midterm but only got a 59%! Not recommended, unless you have a photographic memory.
